Package: fastlane-generate-envelope
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Fastlane Labs <info@fastlane-labs.com>
Description: Fastlane Generate Envelope - Delegation envelope generator for Monad Validators
 Command-line utility to generate delegation envelopes for Monad validators.
 Creates encrypted sidecar keystores and properly signed (or unsigned) delegation
 envelopes for use with the Fastlane MEV sidecar.
